## Examples  
 下列範例會處理<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognitionEngine.SpeechRecognized?displayProperty=nameWithType>或<xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SpeechRecognizer.SpeechRecognized?displayProperty=nameWithType>事件和主控台相關資訊的可辨識音訊會與辨識結果相關聯的輸出。  
  
```csharp  
  
// Handle the SpeechRecognized event.   
void SpeechRecognizedHandler(object sender, SpeechRecognizedEventArgs e)  
